Ebola Haemorrhagic Fever In Uganda - Update 6
---------------------------------------------
As of Sun 22 Oct 2000, the Ugandan Ministry of Health has reported 149
cases, including 54 deaths. [This represents an increase of 10 cases and 3
deaths in the last 24 hours. - Mod.CP
